data.description: Don't miss the chance to make this stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with nice sized closets throughout your very own! Backyard ready to entertain family and friends offering above ground pool with deck and extended covered patio. This one you will not want to miss! Also, in Cooper District. Schedule a showing today!
